/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/gradient_maker_pool_1777191969/final_report.md:209:**Impact:** A router migration or registry misconfiguration can permanently DOS orderbook transfers and fee distributions for already-live pools, and later deposits can be priced against the wrong market. This can freeze trading/reward flows for existing LPs or misprice new liquidity against unrelated reserves.
