/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uniclynft_p5_25_124/foundry_validation/F-001_ERC1155_mint_callback_reentrancy_lets_co/codex_stderr_attempt3.log:6740:/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/uniclynft_p5_25_124/rounds/round_1/round_summary_stderr.log:743:[{"id":"F-001","severity":"Critical","confidence":"high","title":"Reward Theft via Emergency Withdraw Without Pool Update","locations":["Contract.sol:1615-1623"],"claim":"The emergencyWithdraw() function does not call updatePool() before transferring tokens, causing the pool's accPointsPerShare to become stale.","impact":"An attacker can steal rewards from other users by: 1) depositing tokens, 2) calling emergencyWithdraw to remove their stake without updating pool state, 3) waiting for other users to trigger updatePool via deposit, which calculates rewards based on stale accPointsPerShare. The attacker will receive disproportionately high rewards because the pool's token balance decreased but accPointsPerShare did not increase proportionally.","paths":["1. Attacker deposits into pool using deposit()","2. Attacker calls emergencyWithdraw() to get tokens back without calling updatePool()","3. Legitimate user calls deposit(), which triggers updatePool()","4. Attacker calls withdraw() or deposit() to claim pending rewards","5. Attacker receives inflated reward due to stale accPointsPerShare"]},{"id":"F-002","severity":"High","confidence":"high","title":"Uninitialized Shop Variable Causes Contract Lock","locations":["Contract.sol:1465","Contract.sol:1510-1511"],"claim":"The shop variable is declared but never initialized in the constructor, defaulting to address(0). The add() function requires msg.sender == shop, which can never be satisfied.","impact":"The contract cannot add new pools unless the owner sets the shop address via setShop(). If the owner loses access to their wallet or fails to set the shop, the protocol becomes permanently locked with no ability to add new liquidity pools.","paths":["1. Contract is deployed with shop = address(0)","2. Any user attempts to call add() - transaction reverts","3. If owner doesn't call setShop(), no pools can ever be added"]},{"id":"F-003","severity":"High","confidence":"medium","title":"Missing Pool ID Bounds Check","locations":["Contract.sol:1576","Contract.sol:1596","Contract.sol:1615","Contract.sol:1535"],"claim":"Functions deposit(), withdraw(), emergencyWithdraw(), and pendingPoints() access poolInfo[_pid] without validating that _pid is within bounds.","impact":"An out-of-bounds pool ID will cause a revert due to invalid array access, potentially causing DOS for legitimate users who mistype a pool ID. Additionally, reading past array bounds could return stale data from other storage slots.","paths":["1. User calls deposit() with _pid = 100 when only 5 pools exist","2. Transaction reverts with out-of-bounds error","3. User loses gas and transaction fails"]},{"id":"F-004","severity":"Medium","confidence":"high","title":"Precision Loss in Reward Distribution","locations":["Contract.sol:1542","Contract.sol:1569","Contract.sol:1581","Contract.sol:1601"],"cff    128 Mar 13 16:47 0xa5564a2d1190a141CAC438c9fde686aC48a18A79\ndrwxr-xr-x    5 zhanglongqin  staff    160 Mar 20 15:13 0xa88800cd213da5ae406ce248380802bd53b47647\ndrwxr-xr-x    3 zhanglongqin  staff     96 Mar 14 22:37 0xae60aC8e69414C2Dc362D0e6a03af643d1D85b92\ndrwxr-xr-x    3 zhanglongqin  staff     96 Mar 13 15:47 0xaf274e912243b19B882f02d731dacd7CD13072D0\ndrwxr-xr-x    3 zhanglongqin  staff     96 Mar 13 22:02 0xb0f8Fe96b4880adBdEDE0dDF446bd1e7EF122C4e\ndrwxr-xr-x    3 zhanglongqin  staff     96 Mar 12 15:42 0xb276647E70CB3b81a1cA302Cf8DE280fF0cE5799\ndrwxr-xr-x    4 zhanglongqin  staff    128 Mar 13 00:54 0xb5599f568D3f3e6113B286d010d2BCa40A7745AA\ndrwxr-xr-x    4 zhanglongqin  staff    128 Mar 16 00:33 0xb57E874082417b66877429481473CF9FCd8e0b8a\ndrwxr-xr-x    3 zhanglongqin  staff     96 Mar 15 00:43 0xbAa87546cF87b5De1b0b52353A86792D40b8BA70\ndrwxr-xr-x    3 zhanglo